# Db2-LargeTableYearSplit — Log Gathering and Monitoring

## When the user asks to check logs, status, or errors

**Always run the status-gathering script first**, then analyze the locally copied files:

```powershell
pwsh.exe -NoProfile -File "C:\opt\src\DedgePsh\DevTools\DatabaseTools\Db2-LargeTableYearSplit\Get-SplitJobStatus.ps1" -ServerName "<server>" -DaysBack <n>
```

Default server: `t-no1fkmmig-db`. Adjust `-DaysBack` based on the user's request.

## After running the script

Log files are copied to `$env:TEMP\SplitJobStatus\`. Use these local copies for all further analysis:

| File pattern | Content |
|---|---|
| `app_YYYYMMDD.log` | App-specific log from `\\<server>\opt\data\Db2-LargeTableYearSplit\` |
| `central_YYYYMMDD.log` | Central PowerShell log from `\\<server>\opt\data\AllPwshLog\` |
| `orch_stdout.txt` | Orchestrator live output (if present) |
| `orch_result.json` | Orchestrator result (if present) |

**Never read UNC paths directly.** Always use the local copies in `$env:TEMP\SplitJobStatus\`.

## Key log patterns to search for

| Pattern | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `JOB_STARTED\|JOB_COMPLETED\|JOB_FAILED` | Job boundaries and duration |
| `\|ERROR\|` | All errors |
| `RenameAndReload COMPLETE` | Successful R&R completion |
| `Total rows.*Rows to KEEP` | Pre-split row counts |
| `New DBM\.` | Post-split row counts |
| `_TMP.*rows` | TMP table status |
| `EXPORT complete` | IXF file size and timing |
| `LOAD complete` | Load timing and row verification |
| `SQL0104N\|SQL0750N\|SQL1013N\|DB21034E` | Common Db2 errors |
| `Cannot index into a null` | PowerShell array handling bug |

## Creating ExecLogs reports

Place execution reports in:

```
DevTools/DatabaseTools/Db2-LargeTableYearSplit/ExecLogs/<servername>_<yyyyMMdd-HHmmss>.md
```

Use the Shadow Pipeline ExecLog format as a template (see `Db2-ShadowDatabase/ExecLogs/`).

## Deploy and run

Deploy: `pwsh.exe -NoProfile -File "C:\opt\src\DedgePsh\DevTools\DatabaseTools\Db2-LargeTableYearSplit\_deploy.ps1"`

Run via orchestrator:
```powershell
. "C:\opt\src\DedgePsh\DevTools\CodingTools\Cursor-ServerOrchestrator\_helpers\_CursorAgent.ps1"
Invoke-ServerCommand -ServerName '<server>' -Command '%OptPath%\DedgePshApps\Db2-LargeTableYearSplit\Db2-LargeTableYearSplit.ps1' -Project 'large-table-split' -Timeout 86400
```

## Tables and config

Config file: `ArchiveTables.json` — defines tables, timestamp columns, and methods.
Methods: `ExportLoad` (per-year export+load+delete), `RenameAndReload` (rename original, create new, load kept rows).

